pullRequest.title: Implement a basic PlaceholderService
pullRequest.bodyText:
Sponge API | SpongeCommon (that's here!) |  SpongeDocs
Simple implementation of the placeholder API. See API PR for more details.

Also, moved economy registry modules in Common into a service package to make it clear they are from services.
